Operatons:

push, pop, top

empty - returns true if stack is empty
full - return true if stack is full

intialize


implement an adt stack stackadt.h file. the .h file will contain a stack datatype definition 
and the code of all stack functions and displayStack().

use the following preprocessor statements:

#ifndef STACK_H
#define STACK_H
// definition
$endif

create a driver program, that includes the stackadt.h file, checks and uses the operations defined in stackadt.h


make:

stackADT_array.h & stackADT_linkedList.h 


typedef struct {
    char elem[max];
    int top;
}stack



typedef struct node {
    char data;
    struct node* next;
}*stack